Good morning, boys.

454
00:31:59,313 --> 00:32:02,714
Sorry, I am so late.

455
00:32:02,884 --> 00:32:04,749
That's fine. We only just got here.

456
00:32:04,919 --> 00:32:06,978
Forty-five minutes ago.

457
00:32:07,154 --> 00:32:08,951
Howie, are these your kids?

458
00:32:10,057 --> 00:32:11,991
You know, I've never actually met them.

459
00:32:12,159 --> 00:32:14,787
They are good-Iooking boys.

460
00:32:14,962 --> 00:32:18,796
That's a girl. That's Sue and Paul.

461
00:32:19,901 --> 00:32:22,836
Yes, so it is.

462
00:32:23,004 --> 00:32:26,997
You know what?
She is gonna be a heartbreaker.

463
00:32:27,341 --> 00:32:29,639
That's Paul.

464
00:32:29,810 --> 00:32:32,574
- Yeah. Thank you.
