465
00:32:35,016 --> 00:32:37,780
So we've got the Coney Island project.

466
00:32:37,952 --> 00:32:40,921
I'd like to stir up some publicity if we could.

467
00:32:44,191 --> 00:32:46,352
Yes, very nice.

468
00:32:49,597 --> 00:32:51,360
I'm...

469
00:32:53,534 --> 00:32:57,561
I'm working on endorsements
from local merchants.

470
00:33:05,645 --> 00:33:10,048
We were working
on some ideas there.

471
00:33:13,186 --> 00:33:14,585
I thought that was terrific.

472
00:33:16,956 --> 00:33:18,446
- Pathetic.
- What's pathetic?

473
00:33:18,625 --> 00:33:21,560
- You. I know what you're doing.
